- Create a VM using Bitnami Jenkins VM
- Navigate to the VM and change the user password
	- Navigate to the url
	- login with user/bitnami
	- click UserName at the top
	- go to configure
	- update the password field

- Integrate with github: http://fourkitchens.com/blog/2011/09/20/trigger-jenkins-builds-pushing-github

- Install Violation plugin: https://wiki.jenkins-ci.org/display/JENKINS/Violations

- install node.js plugin: https://wiki.jenkins-ci.org/display/JENKINS/NodeJS+Plugin

- Setup "E-mail Notification" using gmail
	- smtp server: smtp.gmail.com
	- use smtp authentication
	- username: your email
	- password: your password
	- use ssl true
	smtp: 465
	test the email configuration

